                                            <p class="pt-0000008648c8d9-dd51-46e0-ba6b-e624de966187" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({R}_{1}=ρ\frac{{l}_{1}}{{A}_{1}}………\left(i\right);\ {R}_{2}=ρ\frac{{l}_{2}}{{A}_{2}}………\left(ii\right);\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018648c8d9-dd51-46e0-ba6b-e624de966187"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008648c8d9-dd51-46e0-ba6b-e624de966187 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018648c8d9-dd51-46e0-ba6b-e624de966187 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002e40f51f-dcb0-475a-823e-5b0609c1c80f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({R}_{1}={R}_{2}⇒ρ\frac{{l}_{1}}{{A}_{1}}=ρ\frac{{l}_{2}}{{A}_{2}}⇒\frac{{l}_{1}}{{l}_{2}}=\frac{{A}_{1}}{{A}_{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e40f51f-dcb0-475a-823e-5b0609c1c80f"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e40f51f-dcb0-475a-823e-5b0609c1c80f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002e40f51f-dcb0-475a-823e-5b0609c1c80f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012e40f51f-dcb0-475a-823e-5b0609c1c80f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c3d35ab2-1ac6-4ff7-9b71-b23a2ebaa891" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{3}{4}=\frac{\frac{π}{4}{d}_{1}^{2}}{\frac{π}{4}\ {d}_{2}^{2}}⇒\frac{{d}_{1}}{{d}_{2}}=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}∴{d}_{1}:{d}_{2}=\sqrt{3}:2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c3d35ab2-1ac6-4ff7-9b71-b23a2ebaa891"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c