                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6">mgvKjb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6"> Ki:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{{x}^{2}dx}{{x}^{4}-1}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000003d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000003d742f354-cdbc-4f94-8dac-68f9fd1e34e6 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
