                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 20</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000004681e6bb-ba8d-4027-8259-6f8ee3bdc939" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014681e6bb-ba8d-4027-8259-6f8ee3bdc939">Correct the dangling modifier. </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004681e6bb-ba8d-4027-8259-6f8ee3bdc939 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000014681e6bb-ba8d-4027-8259-6f8ee3bdc939 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9">(a) After listening to the lecture, the notes were complete.</span><span class="pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9"><br />‎(b) While waiting for the bus, the storm broke out.</span><span class="pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9"><br />‎(c) Hoping to catch the train, the ticket was purchased quickly by her.</span><span class="pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9"><br />‎(d) Looking through the microscope, the specimen was moving.</span><span class="pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9"><br />‎(e) To solve the problem, more effort was given by us.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001f3873101-8412-40a7-8c74-fe7d50ac10b9 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-0000005ad09aef-12fe-4854-8f21-e6d53b01407a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000015ad09aef-12fe-4854-8f21-e6d53b01407a">(</span><span class="pt-0000015ad09aef-12fe-4854-8f21-e6d53b01407a">a) After listening to the lecture, I completed the notes.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005ad09aef-12fe-4854-8f21-e6d53b01407a {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000015ad09aef-12fe-4854-8f21-e6d53b01407a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005ab70c13-f0bc-4188-a5de-4bfd291cdc12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000015ab70c13-f0bc-4188-a5de-4bfd291cdc12">or, I completed the notes after listening to the lecture.</span><span class="pt-0000015ab70c13-f0bc-4188-a5de-4bfd291cdc12"><br />‎(b) While waiting for the bus, I saw the storm break out.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005ab70c13-f0bc-4188-a5de-4bfd291cdc12 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000015ab70c13-f0bc-4188-a5de-4bfd291cdc12 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008c2d038e-def8-491a-8b2c-1fe630a4fa41" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000018c2d038e-def8-491a-8b2c-1fe630a4fa41">or, As I waited for the bus, a storm suddenly broke out.</span><span class="pt-0000018c2d038e-def8-491a-8b2c-1fe630a4fa41"><br />‎(c) Hoping to catch the train, she purchased the ticket quickly.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008c2d038e-def8-491a-8b2c-1fe630a4fa41 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000018c2d038e-def8-491a-8b2c-1fe630a4fa41 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac">or, </span><span class="pt-0000011f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac">She</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac"> quickly purchased the ticket, hoping to catch the train.</span><span class="pt-0000011f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac"><br />‎(d) Looking through the microscope, I saw the specimen moving.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000011f621ef7-4161-4be1-b039-bb44fdd5a3ac {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cc74aa30-2b60-48b6-b336-02c55b8c2e89" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001cc74aa30-2b60-48b6-b336-02c55b8c2e89">or, When I looked through the microscope, I noticed the specimen moving.</span><span class="pt-000001cc74aa30-2b60-48b6-b336-02c55b8c2e89"><br />‎(e) To solve the problem, we gave more effort.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cc74aa30-2b60-48b6-b336-02c55b8c2e89 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001cc74aa30-2b60-48b6-b336-02c55b8c2e89 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589">or, </span><span class="pt-000001a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589">We</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589"> put in more effort to solve the problem.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001a3965ef1-c713-4013-aa9b-62d8ca2d1589 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000bc19ea1-d2b9-409a-a3e6-fe9a6181ce3c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010bc19ea1-d2b9-409a-a3e6-fe9a6181ce3c">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000bc19ea1-d2b9-409a-a3e6-fe9a6181ce3c {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000010bc19ea1-d2b9-409a-a3e6-fe9a6181ce3c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ae191e70-6815-4d38-acdb-41798dcbc0d6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ae191e70-6815-4d38-acdb-41798dcbc0d6">(0.5</span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\times \) </span><span class="pt-000001ae191e70-6815-4d38-acdb-41798dcbc0d6">5) = 2.5 marks for writing the correct dangling modifier.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ae191e70-6815-4d38-acdb-41798dcbc0d6 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001ae191e70-6815-4d38-acdb-41798dcbc0d6 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 21</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000cad60a8a-748f-4a88-a621-6aebeff37335" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001cad60a8a-748f-4a88-a621-6aebeff37335">Make meaningful sentences with the following words:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cad60a8a-748f-4a88-a621-6aebeff37335 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001cad60a8a-748f-4a88-a621-6aebeff37335 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a9250265-e4cf-453c-b001-78f071997f46" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a9250265-e4cf-453c-b001-78f071997f46">Huntsman, Solemn, Relentless, Adamant, Evade</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a9250265-e4cf-453c-b001-78f071997f46 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001a9250265-e4cf-453c-b001-78f071997f46 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-0000002bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000012bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177">Huntsman:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000022bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177"> The huntsman went deep into the forest to find deer.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000012bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000022bdfe71c-bf24-4a5a-a19f-9bfb7636e177 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000043167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000143167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0">Solemn:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000243167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0"> He swore a solemn oath to keep faith.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000043167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000143167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000243167c4e-64ea-469b-b564-4f966f6d43f0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000035c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000135c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d">Relentless:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000235c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d"> She showed relentless courage against her father’s wrongdoing. </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000035c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000135c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000235c7d66e-d7bf-409b-8744-fd01e6f79b6d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33">Adamant: </span><span class="pt-000002e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33">She remained adamant in her stand.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002e716d189-c4b9-47f2-b6ff-410eaeec9c33 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000020aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000120aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a">Evade:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000220aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a"> The corrupted people always try to evade taxes.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000020aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000120aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000220aaace9-6634-4360-95a6-f53df04d581a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007c9812b7-a97a-4412-9d3a-6ee3afe9fdb6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000017c9812b7-a97a-4412-9d3a-6ee3afe9fdb6">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007c9812b7-a97a-4412-9d3a-6ee3afe9fdb6 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000017c9812b7-a97a-4412-9d3a-6ee3afe9fdb6 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000bc31ce5c-dc36-40cd-a997-46ec9c8f75d9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left(0.5\times 5\right)=2.5\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001bc31ce5c-dc36-40cd-a997-46ec9c8f75d9"> marks for making any meaningful and correct sentences.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000bc31ce5c-dc36-40cd-a997-46ec9c8f75d9 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001bc31ce5c-dc36-40cd-a997-46ec9c8f75d9 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 22</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-00000060d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000160d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159">Write a paragraph on </span><span class="pt-00000260d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159">“Importance of Mental Health Awareness”</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000160d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159"> within 100 words.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000060d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000160d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000260d9930e-b686-4358-aaba-352b0fe71159 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-00000060e902ff-2e9d-478e-b830-2faad8197b88" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000160e902ff-2e9d-478e-b830-2faad8197b88">Importance of Mental Health Awareness</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000060e902ff-2e9d-478e-b830-2faad8197b88 {margin-bottom: 0;text-align: center;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000160e902ff-2e9d-478e-b830-2faad8197b88 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000378d6a30-f188-49d7-887f-fcad8e012b75" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001378d6a30-f188-49d7-887f-fcad8e012b75">Mental health awareness is the understanding and recognition of psychological well-being and mental disorders. It is essential because awareness helps in early identification and treatment of mental health issues such as stress, anxiety, and depression. Lack of awareness can result in severe consequences, including social isolation, low productivity, and stigma, which often prevents individuals from seeking help. </span><span class="pt-000001378d6a30-f188-49d7-887f-fcad8e012b75">Promoting mental health awareness encourages open conversations, reduces misconceptions, and creates supportive environments in schools, workplaces, and communities. Governments, healthcare providers, and educational institutions organize counseling programs, workshops, and campaigns to educate people about coping strategies and preventive measures. By prioritizing mental health, society ensures better emotional balance, stronger interpersonal relationships, and overall well-being. Increasing awareness also fosters empathy, inclusion, and resilience, making individuals and communities healthier, happier, and more productive in their daily lives.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000378d6a30-f188-49d7-887f-fcad8e012b75 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001378d6a30-f188-49d7-887f-fcad8e012b75 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000009bf2c7f2-02df-4a20-bc4d-e8fcad2964c9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009bf2c7f2-02df-4a20-bc4d-e8fcad2964c9 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000072fe7a0d-5d5f-4ae6-9619-eb1e7c86932d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000172fe7a0d-5d5f-4ae6-9619-eb1e7c86932d">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000072fe7a0d-5d5f-4ae6-9619-eb1e7c86932d {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000172fe7a0d-5d5f-4ae6-9619-eb1e7c86932d {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000058ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000158ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0">0.5 mark for writing Title “</span><span class="pt-00000258ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0">Importance of Mental Health Awareness”</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000058ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000158ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000258ccb2ad-0a6d-4cd1-a8d6-8a1602d1f3f0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000004e33d28f-aa3c-42ec-9816-b6344d0f938c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000014e33d28f-aa3c-42ec-9816-b6344d0f938c">0.5 mark for writing the definition of mental health awareness.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004e33d28f-aa3c-42ec-9816-b6344d0f938c {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000014e33d28f-aa3c-42ec-9816-b6344d0f938c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c98a62ea-e316-42ed-847e-b195a7534bf0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001c98a62ea-e316-42ed-847e-b195a7534bf0">01 mark for writing the necessity of mental health awareness.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c98a62ea-e316-42ed-847e-b195a7534bf0 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001c98a62ea-e316-42ed-847e-b195a7534bf0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003c44afb6-53d8-43ae-802a-e61b3c4a6460" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000013c44afb6-53d8-43ae-802a-e61b3c4a6460">01 mark for writing effects of lack of awareness on individuals and society.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003c44afb6-53d8-43ae-802a-e61b3c4a6460 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000013c44afb6-53d8-43ae-802a-e61b3c4a6460 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002dc3ebd2-dc1e-4e75-ae11-2988a99ca4aa" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000012dc3ebd2-dc1e-4e75-ae11-2988a99ca4aa">01 mark for writing efforts to promote mental health awareness.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002dc3ebd2-dc1e-4e75-ae11-2988a99ca4aa {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000012dc3ebd2-dc1e-4e75-ae11-2988a99ca4aa {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000e5a57217-7db1-4577-b490-7581fd90ca69" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001e5a57217-7db1-4577-b490-7581fd90ca69">01 mark for writing effects of promote mental health awareness.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e5a57217-7db1-4577-b490-7581fd90ca69 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001e5a57217-7db1-4577-b490-7581fd90ca69 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586">[</span><span class="pt-000002f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586">Instructions:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-000001f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002f2beb853-f266-4861-8d13-bc4c2d4e6586 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000008a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000108a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">* Students must write it within one single para. If it becomes </span><span class="pt-00000208a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">more than one para</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000108a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">, </span><span class="pt-00000208a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">50% marks</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000108a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84"> have to be </span><span class="pt-00000208a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">deducted</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000108a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84"> from the </span><span class="pt-00000208a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84">obtained marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000008a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000108a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000208a3ce30-d4cf-45a5-a9c4-b88a4866be84 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000030877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1">* </span><span class="pt-00000230877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1">Students must write it within 100 words limit.</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1"> </span><span class="pt-00000230877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1">For exceeding the</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1"> 100 words limit, 0.5 marks</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000230877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1"> have to be </span><span class="pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1">deducted</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000230877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1"> from the </span><span class="pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1">deserved marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000030877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000130877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000230877d87-cddf-4d11-801d-67c0c61695c1 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000003609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000103609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0">* 0.5 mark will be </span><span class="pt-00000203609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0">deducted for one or two grammar or spelling mistakes</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000103609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0">, 01 mark </span><span class="pt-00000203609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0">for three or more grammar or spelling mistakes</span><span class="pt-00000103609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0">.]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000003609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000103609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000203609b07-9fb2-43e4-8dd6-f31101f894a0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
